style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:10px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a> housing.<br />\nThe homeownership rate in America has now dropped to 63.7 percent,<a class=\"icouskoimj\" title=\"Click to Continue &gt; by FlashMall\" href=\"#19731417\"> according<span class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:10px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a> to the U.S. Census, down from 69+ percent peak in 2004.<br />\nBecause of that, rental apartment occupancy is now at an all-time high, and rents are rising at <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">twice the pace of inflation</span>. In turn, that is putting pressure on renters young and old, but not necessarily pushing them to the pursuit of home ownership. Higher rents make it more difficult to save for a<a class=\"icouskoimj\" title=\"Click to Continue &gt; by FlashMall\" href=\"#69442224\"> down payment<span class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:10px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a>. <a href=\"https://thepmgrp.com/agency-news/bad-news-for-millennials-as-affordable-housing-is-scarce/\">Millennials today</a> find themselves spending more on housing than their parents did.<br />\n<strong><em>More than half of U.S. residents report having had to make at least one sacrifice or tradeoff in the past three years to cover their rent or<a class=\"icouskoimj\" title=\"Click to Continue &gt; by FlashMall\" href=\"#73194105\"> mortgage<span class=\" inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:10px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:100%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcSet=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 10px) 100vw, 10px\" srcset=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/ea982/arrow-10x10.png 3w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/cf79e/arrow-10x10.png 5w,\n/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png 10w\" src=\"/static/62f9c7e06ff8660c885658a1b4b7d178/65364/arrow-10x10.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span></a>, and the highest segment of those sacrificing is renters (73 percent)…. according to a report by the MacArthur Foundation.</em></strong><br />\nOf course, this has led to sluggish U.S. retail performance as more disposable income is required to pay for higher rents. The proof is in the numbers. This has certainly been the case over the last several quarters as many retailers are finding it more difficult to achieve profitable sales.</p>\n","title":"Higher Rental Housing Costs Mean More Economic Pain for the Middle Class","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"Higher Rental Housing Costs Mean More Economic Pain for the Middle Class","url":"/more-economic-pain-for-the-middle-class/"}],"title":"More Economic Pain for the Middle Class | The PM Group","metaDesc":"Middle-class Americans are still challenged with finding affordable rental housing. What effect will this have on homeownership and the real estate mar